calculate_hash // false

-revise prompt/sampler/seed
-moderate step/batch/prompt size

-edit flow beginning at VRAMs 
-facedetail on, upscale off
-perform inpainting needs
-moderate guide sizes
[ S T A G E  3 ]
-edit flow beginning at VRAM step 
-facedetail off, upscale on
-moderate rescale factor

[ C H A N G E  M O D E L  V E R ]
-adjust model, vae, clips, vaenamer

[ C U D A  O U T  O F  M E M ]

- look beneath sdpromptsaver
- toggle gc_collect/unload
- run, then toggle again
- don't empty cache after sampler
